	<TABLE><TR><TD><IMG SRC="graphics/button.gif" ALIGN="TOP"></TD><TD><FONT FACE=" Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" SIZE=+1 COLOR="#000000"><A NAME="200034100I"><B>Velious Emergency Patches</B></A></FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD ALIGN="left"><FONT FACE=" Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" SIZE=+1 COLOR="#000000">2000-12-07</FONT></TD><TD></TD></TR></TABLE><TABLE><TR><TD><FONT FACE=" Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" SIZE=2 COLOR="#000000"><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="arial, verdana">
The servers are up and down today, as they are doing some emergency patches to Velious. Apparently, some god loot has dropped on the wrong mobs (*again*) and they are fixing that with an item change. No official ETA on when the patches will be done, but in chat I heard a GM say the average time for each server seems to be 45 mins or so.<BR><BR>
Also, the screenshot of Velious I have posted (upper right of this window) is my first look at the Velious continent! This is where you port to when a wizard uses their Iceclad portal spell. Unfortunately, after successfully killing a few blue Frost Giants and Snow Dervishes, we were set upon by a Snow Guardian (red to me at 36) and suffered a quick death *grin*. We will be back for revenge, never fear!<BR><BR>
